Adewale Adeyinka (amụrụ na 14 Disemba 1996) bụ onye Naijiria na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba dịka onye na-edebe goolu maka Kwara United na ndị otu mba Naijiria. Ọ bụbu onye egwuregwu Naịjirịa U17
Adeyinka meriri Ọkachamara bọọlụ Naịjirịa League na Akwa United na oge 2020-21.
Nwa amaala Kwara nwere ihe ndekọ maka ọtụtụ mpempe akwụkwọ dị ọcha na Nigeria Professional Football League, mgbe ọ gachara egwuregwu iri na isii n'enyeghị ihe mgbaru ọsọ na oge 2020-21.
